{"tid":1074364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國限古令發威！上半年古裝劇全泡湯","createTime":"2019-03-23T10:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T12:36:58.000Z","uid":64191,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50ce040b64d1e8486ae67714d09e0114b9efdb3e","tid":1074364,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"記者吳孟倫／台北報導〕去年中國宮鬥劇《延禧攻略》及《如懿傳》接續發威，讓清宮劇再度掀起熱潮，但卻讓中國政府相當不滿，認為帶壞社會風氣下令停播，但成效不彰。今（22）日有人爆料史上最嚴的禁古令即將來襲，即日起至6月古裝劇一律不許上檔。<br />\n<br />\n此次的限古令主要針對武俠、玄幻、歷史、神話、穿越、傳記、宮鬥等類型的戲劇，由於第一季度宮鬥調控各家執行力度不夠，第二季度要嚴格執行，網路上已上線的古裝劇將撤掉所有版面，未播的另外擇日排播，受到影響的有王一博的《陳情令》、易烊千璽的《長安十二時辰》、張若昀的《慶餘年》、秦俊傑的《天下長安》、譚松韻的《錦衣之下》，王大陸主演的《狼殿下》也是受害者之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外有業界人士透露金馬影后章子怡首度主演的電視劇《帝王業》也會受限古令牽連，而《延禧攻略》中的「攻略」太過敏感，往後不允許電視劇再使用這兩字，恰巧先前于正宣布新劇《盛唐攻略》改名為《大唐女兒行》，間接證實了這項消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2735977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2735977&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=76cae806\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2735977&h=679bc2f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2735977</a><br />\n而家連「攻略」都唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13e970691672a682964075a385efd2a8c679fef","tid":1074364,"uid":64191,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"最大規模既中國「去中國化」開始了"},{"pid":"fed4466922ae1f0e7c51fde1191b3cf31128d85f","tid":1074364,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"等等又話乜乜女兒行又影射邊柒個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966627decdcc06131059bb88e98f73dff349af9f","tid":1074364,"uid":194012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"中國有五千年歷史 但係有4950年都唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f29d86fbff7deb231a9e81093b7189d8564535","tid":1074364,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T11:09:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"157f1f677f9910a9a7ff16a130f5d2f9ec0eb976","tid":1074364,"uid":23832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T12:36:58.000Z","msg":"啱㗎喇<br />\n支那狗就適合睇返樣板戲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p70AiVb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp70AiVb.png&h=05dda45f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ckouomT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FckouomT.png&h=b8baba33&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}